@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mdviss(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.72
    v0 = (0.20 * 0.19)
    v1 = 0.08
    v0 = v2
    v1 = (wp.abs(v1) - (0.73 * (v2 + 0.14 - v0 + 0.37)))
    tmp = (v1 / ((v0 + 0.26 + tmp + 0.80) + 0.52))
    tmp = v0
    v0 = 0.92
    data[tid] = v0
